application_type_full: Outline planning permission: Some matters reserved
description: Demolition of existing buildings; erection of a four storey block comprising a multi purpose community hall/resource centre/disability centre (Classes D1 Non Residential Institutions and D2 Assembly and Leisure) and 26 two bedroom, 4 three bedroom and 6 one bedroom flats; erection of a three/four storey building with basement parking comprising 46 two bedroom, 26 one bedroom and 4 three bedroom flats and a three storey building with parking under comprising 4 two bedroom flats (total gross floor area of buildings 12,077 M2; alterations to vehicular access and provision of associated parking
